            "example": [
                {
                    "text": "With six sides on a die, the "
                },
                {
                    "text": "probability",
                    "colorize": true
                },
                {
                    "text": " of rolling a three is one in six, or about 17 percent"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Math/science term. 'High probability' = likely to happen. 'Low probability' = unlikely. Not the same as 'possibility' (something could happen) vs. 'probability' (how likely it is)."
        },
