                {
                    "text": "human error",
                    "colorize": true
                },
                {
                    "text": " — someone entered the wrong coordinates into the navigation system"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Common phrase in engineering, medicine, and aviation to distinguish person-caused failures from mechanical ones. Often used defensively: 'It wasn't the software's fault—it was human error.'"
        },
